These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, musical
3 different pets are kept: hamster, chinchilla, fish
1. the owner of the fish is somewhere between the person watching adventure movies and the owner of the chinchilla##7
2. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
3. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | horror | adventure |
| Pet           | chinchilla  | fish     | hamster  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, dubstep, rock
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, airplane, ship
1. the person driving the trike is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of r&b is somewhere between the fan of rock and the person driving the airplane##7
3. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | r&b | rock |
| Transport     | airplane       | ship     | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, juice
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, car, boat
1. the person driving the car is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person driving the motorbike##7
2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Beverage    | milk | iced-tea | juice  |
| Transport   | boat  | car  | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, librarian, entrepreneur
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, crime, satire
1. the bartender is somewhere between the person watching satire movies and the librarian##7
2. the person watching crime movies is not the bartender##6
3. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching crime movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Job           | librarian | bartender | entrepreneur     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime    | family          | satire |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, folk, soul
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, bus, taxi
1. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person driving the taxi and the fan of folk##7
2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the fan of soul##1
3. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | blues      | soul     | folk   |
| Transport     | taxi | bus | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, d&b, dubstep
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, australian, russian
1. the dutch is on the left or right of the australian##3
2. the australian is somewhere to the left of the dutch##5
3. the fan of d&b is on the right of the russian##1
4. the fan of d&b is somewhere between the russian and the fan of pop##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | d&b     | pop     |
| Nationality   | russian | australian | dutch |

