.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
3 different pets are kept: snake, hamster, bird
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, snowboarding, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the owner of the snake and the person who's sport is tennis##7
3. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Pet     | bird       | hamster      | snake       |
| Sport   | tennis | biathlon | snowboarding |

