.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-8::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, bartender, software-developer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, action, zombie
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the musician##3
2. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere between the person watching zombie movies and the bartender##7
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Job           | software-developer | musician  | bartender |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie      | time-travel | action      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, reading, woodworking
The people have 3 different jobs:  social-worker, dancer, musician
1. the musician is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6
2. the dancer is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the social-worker is somewhere between the dancer and the person who's hobby is reading##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | reading | woodworking | dancing   |
| Job     | musician    | social-worker  | dancer |

