.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, fanta, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, lacrosse
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person who's sport is rugby##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | fanta   | hot-chocolate    | mirinda |
| Sport      | lacrosse | biathlon | rugby |

