.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-11::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, chess, collecting
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, nigerian, chinese
1. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere between the nigerian and the russian##7
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the russian is not the person who's hobby is collecting##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | collecting | reading | chess |
| Nationality   | nigerian    | chinese    | russian         |

