.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-12::.
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, orange, apricot
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, satire, epic
1. the person watching satire movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere between the person watching satire movies and the person eating cucumber##7
3. the person eating orange is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food          | cucumber  | apricot       | orange     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | martial-arts | satire |

