The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, salsa, indie
1. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the fan of jazz and the fan of indie##7
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the fan of salsa is somewhere between the fan of jazz and the person drinking soy-milk##7
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |  3   |
| Beverage      | almond-milk     | 7up | soy-milk |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | salsa    | indie |

