2. the person driving the scooter is the person eating lettuce##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the person eating cabbage##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food        | lettuce | mango | cabbage |
| Transport   | scooter  | skateboard       | bus      |

