.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-16::.
There 3 different types of food: corn, grapes, pepper
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, french, american
1. the person eating corn is somewhere to the right of the person eating pepper##5
2. the person eating pepper is the person eating pepper##1
3. the person eating grapes is somewhere between the american and the polish##7
4. the polish is the person eating corn##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | pepper | grapes     | corn   |
| Nationality   | american   | french | polish |

