.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, juice
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, fisherman, photographer
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the paramedic##1
2. the person drinking juice is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the fisherman##7
3. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the fisherman##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Beverage   | sprite      | juice     | hot-chocolate |
| Job        | photographer | paramedic | fisherman    |

 